title: adidas Skateboarding SF Feature

San Francisco campaign shoot in September 2009 with Mark Gonzales, Dennis Busenitz, Silas Baxter-Neal, Tim O'Connor, Pete Eldridge, Benny Fairfax, Dave Bachinsky, Nestor Judkins, Lem Villemin, Vince del Valle and Jake Donnelly.
